      "raw_text": "Pres. Howard Elliott, OF the\nNorthern Pacific, was in the city\nfor half an hour at noon today,\nleaving for a trip dcSrth Clear\nwater branch, He was accompan-\nled by K. J. Cannon, company at\ntorney, who met him en- route west.\nMr.. Elliott will return tomorrow\nafternoon, when it is expected he\nwill personally take up the grade\nseparation question with city Of\nficials."
